c: 5
v: 82
t: "You will find (E) the strongest people (with) animosity to those who believed (are) the Jews, and those who shared/made partners (with God), and you will find (E) their nearest/closest love/friendship , to those who believed, (are) those who said: \"That we are Christian .\" That (is) with that from them (are) priests/clergymen and monks, and that they are not being arrogant"